  ('catalog-101-essays-that-will-change-the-way-you-think', '101-essays-that-will-change-the-way-you-think', '101 Essays That Will Change the Way You Think', 'A self-help and personal-development pick in mindset & emotional growth, first published in 2016. Popular modern self-reflection essay collection. 101 Essays That Will Change the Way You Think by Brianna Wiest focuses on self help, personal development, and mindset & emotional growth within our Self Help catalogue.', 'self-help', null, null, null, '2016', null, null, 'English', 'Paperback / common retail edition', null, 'curated'),
